body: Because nhentai just mirrors exhentai doujins/manga except that exhentai actually replaces (or expunges) the old gallery if the new one is higher resolution or updates it if the gallery is ongoing translation, while nhentai doesn't REPLACE (or update) so you see these "duplicates" everywhere in nhentai.
I mean it had NTR on the cover so I can't be mad. But why are there so many copies of this on the site.
